week 6 task

*****************************
Docker
*****************************
Docker Install:
Sudo yum install Docker

sudo service docker start |sudo service docker stop | sudo service docker status

adding ec2-user to Docker group:
sudo usermod -a -G docker ec2-user

docker pull image | docker run image [ID]

show running processes:
Docker ps

list available images:
Docker image ls

Run a docker container:
docker run -d -p 80:80 nginx

docker stop [containerID] or [Name]
docker start [containerID] or [Name]
docker logs [containerID] or [Name]
docker image history [image name]
docker rmi [image name]

To login to a docker image:
docker exec -it [containerID] /bin/sh

Docker compose insta: https://docs.docker.com/compose/install/